channel.title: My new non-hamachi server ! (griefers and non-humans not welcome) PhyscoDev v1
channel.description:
[u]Go to bottom if you only wish to see IP.[/u]
Hello people, this is my new non-hamachi server. It's run by me and I am looking for new ops qualified (you must be active and prove to me though) and I hope you guys will join and have an awesome amazing time!! The server will be ran 24/7 (unless updates / maintenece / internet goes down)
The server is non-PVP, monsters on, it has a beautiful world, no whitelist or anything (nothing built yet so build away !!) I will post on a few other websites, MCserverlist, etc.
Only commands are: sethome, home, list I spent hours, time on telus, and almost destroyed my internet (so far only reset all my settings) trying to get it non hamachi but i did it. For you guys xD !
It has little-very little lag, which will hopefully be fixed soon. Hosting on:
3.8GHZ Overclocked quad core 970 Nvidia GeForce GTX 470 over 1MB 8GB Ram 1.5TB Hard disk Windows 7 professional 64-bit
[b]IP: 75.152.217.94 Port: 25565[/b]
